OL,5, A band has postponed their European    
OL,6, tour dates due to the "relentless rise 
OL,7, in touring costs".                     
OL,9,FFerocious Dog, from Nottinghamshire,   
OL,10,Fsaid "inflation had made touring       
OL,11,Fextremely difficult for bands".        
OL,13,FViolinist Dan Booth said they recently 
OL,14,Fspent #6,000 travelling to and         
OL,15,Fperforming two gigs in Poland.         
OL,17,FThe government has been urged to tackle
OL,18,Fthe rising costs of obtaining visas and
OL,19,Ftransporting instruments that musicians
OL,20,Fhave encountered since Brexit.         
